        {
            "title": "Anthropic「Claude Mythos」洩密引發AI恐慌 網路安全股暴跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JkT.J6EQ.Cm0QnT5ytAxjQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7306L_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 網路安全股週五下挫,CrowdStrike(NASDAQ:CRWD)下跌7%,Palo Alto Networks(NASDAQ:PANW)下跌6%,Zscaler(NASDAQ:ZS)下跌4.5%,而Okta(NASDAQ:OKTA)、SentinelOne(NYSE:S)和Fortinet(NASDAQ:FTNT)則下跌3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這波跌勢似乎與Anthropic最新AI模型在發布前遭洩密的報導有關,據《財富》雜誌首先報導,相關描述被儲存在一個可公開存取的數據快取中。關於這款代號為\"Claude Mythos\"的新模型的詳細資訊,據報導被儲存在一份可透過未加密且可公開搜尋的數據儲存庫存取的部落格草稿中。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-827f2b33-97fc-3ebc-970b-aa2a45e3aa9e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家AI新創公司將洩密歸咎於其內容管理系統配置上的\"人為錯誤\"。洩露的草稿介紹了一個名為\"Capybara\"的新AI模型層級,該層級將比Anthropic目前的頂級Opus模型更大、功能更強。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據洩露的文件,與Claude Opus 4.6相比,Capybara在軟體編碼、學術推理和網路安全相關任務方面取得了更高的分數。草稿將Claude Mythos描述為\"我們迄今開發過的最強大AI模型\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic發言人向《財富》雜誌表示,該公司正在\"開發一款在推理、編碼和網路安全方面取得重大進展的通用模型\",並且\"正在審慎考慮如何發布它\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報導,該草稿部落格文章警告稱,該模型\"在網路能力方面遠遠領先於任何其他AI模型\",可能引發\"一波能夠以遠超防禦者努力的方式利用漏洞的模型浪潮\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/anthropic-claude-mythos-%E6%B4%A9%E5%AF%86%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BCai%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C-%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%82%A1%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C-131638208.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-27 21:35:27",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
